snippet.title: Tyler Mann
snippet.description:
I'm a cinematographer and camera operator our of Austin, TX.  My credits include High Profits for CNN/Netflix, My 600 Lb. Life on TLC, Shipping Wars on A&E, North Woods Law on Animal Planet, plus a bunch of others.  I own a RED Gemini package, and FS7 package, and a GoPro Omni 360 VR video package. I've been on tour with platinum selling rock bands (30 Seconds to Mars) and love electric skateboards.

 My personal website:

https://skeeterou.wixsite.com/tylerrmann

My Documentary website: 

http://www.clusterdocumentary.com
